Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.19,0:02:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A child is down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I have to introduce myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this moment onward...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just arrived on the floor right below us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know who or what they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but security has been mobilized.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be safe, the two of you stay there and wait for orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? In a guy's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending someone over to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves you right for inviting yourself into my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh please! If I weren't here, you wouldn't have been able to answer the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, is Elena there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elena?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been trying to contact her using emergency channels, but she's not responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1980, Generation Bleu was founded to protect Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.57,0:03:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should write this down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did not trigger any sensor detections?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my opinion, this is an attack without an official proclamation of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the witnesses say there was only one attacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can this really be treated as such a matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are already fatalities amongst the guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no minor affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you received any intel, Hallström?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. The Americans don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erase all data, transport the IFOs, and secure the pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the absolute worst scenario, destroy {\i1}that{\i0} and the HQ with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Blanc?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't need to be informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0130,,Emergency alert. There's a confirmed intruder in HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0130,,Casualties have also been confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight's gig is cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They told us to hurry to the shelters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there right away! Please go on ahead without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, he's closing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are your intentions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you from, you terrorist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Mirror, right? I'm a huge fan of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask you one more time! Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to my live show, The Ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck it! Shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a singer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you sing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The intruder...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The intruder is heading for the coral—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he gets to the bottom—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:07:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it. He's not going for anything underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Operation of the central shaft cablecar line is fully suspended.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Operation of the central shaft cablecar line is fully suspended.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A temporary stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like something's going on down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're at {\i1}the{\i0} Generation Bleu's headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite the reaction from meeting a nice woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like because we got this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Ao's not the only one getting recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your mouths shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the truth of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:08:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up? You said he's heading upwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The intruder?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yessir. Since his last appearance at the Central Market station,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we haven't been able to track him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But judging from his path so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Graffeud!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strengthen the defense of the central shaft against entry from lower levels!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Order team Pied Piper to scramble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so surprised about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The intruder is heading upwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what we should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying he's going for the IFOs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or the pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if his target is on the lower levels, I'd say an IFO assault would be more effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scramble? Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't even loaded the Nirvash yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if it has to launch alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the Americans here for it or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they can't load you into the Triton on time, you'll have to launch from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing on Nirvash?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvash?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so that's what this machine is called.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what are {\i1}you{\i0} doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in that woman's machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woman? You mean my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from there right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If not—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Rebecka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.01,0:09:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Rebecka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from the base and go somewhere safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvash performed an emergency launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's flying in the 57th tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open Gate A303.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you're using what belongs to that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for having you discharged early from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to see you all in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, I will take command of team Goldilocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Ao?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the moment, Fukai Ao is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stanley!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai Ao is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny! Sis is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I told her to stay in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me she's gone there again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0130,,The island has changed since you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0130,,So it's our fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0130,,It's changed ever since the beginning of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0130,,Having the Allied Forces supervise us is no different from having the Japs on our necks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:12:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one around who still dreams of the Okinawan Archipelago's true independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scub Coral, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the main island had one until Iwato Island received its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The trapar makers jumped on this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The island is as prosperous as it has ever been.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pushing for resistance movements at a time like this will only make me a laughing stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jirou, won't you come back to the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can even succeed me if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your opinion, I've always been "a useless prick."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't start counting on me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm at my limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never seen the truth to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bigwigs are all hiding the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do everything you couldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The island's gonna flourish now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru! You should be in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No buts! What if you get even sicker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get it, go home and be a good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.28,0:13:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't do this! They'll get mad at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my cough is getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to see the Scub Coral, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got this sickness in a Scub Burst, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can get in this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've changed, Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I can't tell at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was Generation Bleu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got nothing to do with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came back because I wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How weird. Breathing isn't hard at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels a lot better when I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done, Naru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that woman's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Fukai Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done to Naru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:17:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So your name is Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvash, we're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what exactly is going—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the sea giant?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to my hometown?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.87,0:17:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you might've been an existence close to the truth of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Naru is even more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru is a normal girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people see nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea giant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru, come here! Get away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? He's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.14,0:19:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even had Noah with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:19:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my sea giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can fly with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is erroneous anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the hospital. You've been out cold for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You flew off with the intruder and crashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:21:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We hurried after you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there were no signs of the intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.27,0:21:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the Mark I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rescue team got you out and brought you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Security Service is chasing after the intruder who made you crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad... So it was just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Rebecka told us not to tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.52,0:21:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is all over the news now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An incident happened on your home island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how much of our budget do you think we pumped into the Mark I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't secure it. There's nothing we can do about it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would say our country should not depend on IFOs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:21:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I just can't accept the fact that \NGeneration Bleu is using the Mark I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.62,0:22:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's funded by our taxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.49,0:22:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we harass them a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.19,0:22:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he infiltrated the headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that was according to our reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He called himself Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He may be the terrorist in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it seems like {\i1}that{\i0} is still under Generation Bleu's headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.86,0:24:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Eureka Seven AO.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Naru was taken from him by his enemy, Ao grows more and more impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.76,0:24:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleur tries to gain strength from her warped feelings for her father in the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.32,0:24:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do they find at the barren land that's at the end of their paths?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.54,0:24:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eureka Seven AO, episode eight: One Nation Under a Groove.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.06,0:24:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to the voices of the children of the stars.
